<li>Dijk, E., Cremer, D.D., Mulder, L.B., and Stouten, J. "How Do We React to Feedback in Social Dilemmas?" In Biel, Eek, Garling &amp; Gustafsson, (eds.), <i>New Issues and Paradigms in Research on Social Dilemmas</i>, New York: Springer, 2008.</li>
</ul>


